{"id":194804,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/11/中国人周二继续资助艾未未缴税单/","date":"2011-11-08T20:31:05Z","modified":"2011-11-08T20:31:05Z","title":"中国人周二继续资助艾未未缴税单","content":"<div>\n<div>\n<p>成千上万中国人星期二继续借款资助艺术家艾未未支付有争议的税单。许多人认为政府发出巨额税单是企图让这位直言不讳的社会批评家沉默。</p>\n<p>在艾未未的北京艺术工作室工作的志愿者表示，目前已经接收到来自海内外两万多笔款项。</p>\n<p>志愿者说，现在资助总额超过560万元人民币。</p>\n<p>艾未未今年早些时候曾在没有控罪的情况下被关押近三个月，随后被指控逃税，被责令在下个星期之前补缴税款约1500万元人民币。</p>\n<p> </p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/BU2rGB1wqgkU0sBrS0jFcglmg14/0/da\"><img src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/BU2rGB1wqgkU0sBrS0jFcglmg14/0/di\" border=\"0\" ismap=\"ismap\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/BU2rGB1wqgkU0sBrS0jFcglmg14/1/da\"><img src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/BU2rGB1wqgkU0sBrS0jFcglmg14/1/di\" border=\"0\" ismap=\"ismap\" /></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/voacn?a=2AD1moncbfU:BJ0UVPOKLH4:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/voacn?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/voacn?a=2AD1moncbfU:BJ0UVPOKLH4:mqyYa2mfVbY\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/voacn?d=mqyYa2mfVbY\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/voacn?a=2AD1moncbfU:BJ0UVPOKLH4:DUWcskeyX7o\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/voacn?d=DUWcskeyX7o\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/voacn?a=2AD1moncbfU:BJ0UVPOKLH4:qj6IDK7rITs\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/voacn?d=qj6IDK7rITs\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/voacn?a=2AD1moncbfU:BJ0UVPOKLH4:clraHZBW0_I\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/voacn?d=clraHZBW0_I\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/voacn?a=2AD1moncbfU:BJ0UVPOKLH4:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/voacn?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/voacn?a=2AD1moncbfU:BJ0UVPOKLH4:R_Hd-r7sPaA\"><img sr